{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/pidfile"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration","role":"symbol","title":"PIDFile","symbolKind":"enum","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}],"externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit7PIDFileO","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Manages PID files for tracking running virtual machines.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/fileName"],"anchor":"Type-Properties","title":"Type Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isProcessAlive(_:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isRunning(bundleURL:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/read(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/remove(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/terminate(bundleURL:gracePeriod:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/write(to:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/writeAndEnsureCapacity(bundleURL:vmDirectory:)"],"anchor":"Type-Methods","title":"Type Methods","generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"typ